I began speedrunning Celeste almost a week ago and initially got a time of 2 hours. That initial run was my first time running the game; I'd only played through it once before - on my initial playthrough.

After 16 runs, I've finally managed to shave the time down to under an hour, which feels like a huge accomplishment for me. This is the first run that I'll be formally submitting to speedrun.com so I've uploaded the video here for all to see.
